{pageend:that are able to enter that contest show.}
Please come back with a Pokémon wearing the
Contest Star Ribbon.

{pageend:Hm?}
It appears that you can’t enter a contest show
{pageend:with that rank.}
Please come back after you’ve successfully
completed a contest show at one rank below.

Thanks for participating! Your Pokémon danced
{pageend:quite well! It’s ready for a real Contest Show!}
Or, would you like to practice dancing again?

You’ve become Star of the Show in every
{pageend:contest show!}
To commemorate your achievement, I’ll present
you with this {tag:0}{pageend:!}
Congratulations!

